when his plan is altered.

834
01:05:14,119 --> 01:05:16,780
He has a fixation for his plans.

835
01:05:16,780 --> 01:05:20,420
Are you already thinking of
a headline, Mr. Kim?

836
01:05:24,889 --> 01:05:27,090
- Hurry up.
- Hey.

837
01:05:28,059 --> 01:05:29,829
