about me.

850
01:06:13,440 --> 01:06:16,710
She doesn't know about my past
or that I'm not normal.

851
01:06:20,380 --> 01:06:21,619
Hyun Su.

852
01:06:22,480 --> 01:06:25,489
How did you become Baek Hee Seong?

853
