857
01:06:38,300 --> 01:06:40,400
I'm positive. Trust me on this.

858
01:06:40,699 --> 01:06:42,039
Mr. Do.

859
01:06:43,969 --> 01:06:45,340
Trust us.

860
01:06:46,139 --> 01:06:47,809
We'll do our best...

861
01:06:48,539 --> 01:06:50,750
